document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Wildcat project in Canada dated October, 2021.pdf
document.description: This report summarizes the technical information and exploration activities conducted on the Wildcat Property, with recommendations for future exploration phases to assess its potential for copper-gold porphyry deposits.
